Guide Firebase hosting 
Link : https://firebase.google.com/docs/hosting
1. Install firebase in command line
    curl -sL https://firebase.tools | bash
2. Create accout on https://firebase.google.com/ and create a project
3. Login
    firebase login
4. Go to directory this you want to do project cd [project_file]
5. Connect the directory to your Firebase project
    firebase init
6. Test run local server before 
    firebase serve
7. Deploy on server public
    firebase deploy
8. Done -> you have a hosting url